interview_instruction:
Here's a sample text for an interview privacy notice:

Subject: Important Notice Regarding Your Interview Privacy

Dear [Candidate Name],

Thank you for your interest in the [Job Title] position at [Company Name]. We value your privacy and want to ensure you understand how we handle your personal information during the interview process.

Information Collected:

During the interview process, we may collect personal information about you, including:

  • Contact Information: Name, phone number, email address, address
  • Professional Information: Resume/CV, cover letter, employment history, education, skills, references
  • Interview Information: Interview notes, assessment results, feedback from interviewers

How We Use Your Information:

We use your information for legitimate business purposes related to the recruitment process, such as:

  • Evaluating your qualifications for the position
  • Communicating with you about the interview process and job opportunities
  • Making hiring decisions
  • Maintaining employment records (if hired)

Data Security:

We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, or alteration. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.   

 

Data Retention:

We will retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined above. We may retain some information for longer periods as required by law or for legitimate business purposes, such as record-keeping and legal compliance.   

 

Your Rights:

You may have certain rights regarding your personal information, such as the right to access, correct, or delete yourinformation. Please contact us at [email address] or [phone number] if you have any questions or requests regarding your privacy.   

 

Third-Party Service Providers:

We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us with the recruitment process, such as background check companies and video conferencing platforms. We require these providers to comply with applicable data protection laws and maintain the confidentiality of your information.

Changes to This Notice:

We may update this Privacy Notice from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated notice on our website or by other appropriate means.
